*Kupi* ga preko interneta (Buy it over the internet).
*Kupovina* je uspješno završena (The purchase was finished successfully).
*Kupio* sam novi automobil (I bought a new car).
*Kupovala* je neke stvari za svoju kuću (She was buying some things for her house).
*Kupuje* se većina namirnica u supermarketu (Most groceries are bought at the supermarket).